name: DUO | Screen - Ceccotti Collezioni
description: The DUO screen consists of 3, 4 or 5 modules with a height of 180 cm, a solid ash wood frame in various finishes and a hollow-core panel. The screen is fully customizable: it is possible to select for the modules either a wallpaper or, upon request, fabric or leather. In addition, the modules can have the two sides with different finishes. The screen feet are adjustable in height thanks to levelers. The metal details are finished in bronzed brass.
